PROJECT NAME: CampusLoop

PROJECT TYPE:
Student Marketplace & Real-Time Communication Platform

IMPORTANT:

Build ONLY the frontend.

DO NOT implement backend logic.
DO NOT create fake database logic.
DO NOT generate server-side code.

Use mock services and frontend state only.

The backend will be implemented separately in Laravel.

